# PaceMap — pacemap.co.uk

Horse racing pace maps for every UK & Irish meeting.

## Tech Stack
- **Next.js 14** (App Router)
- **Clerk** (authentication)
- **Stripe** (payments — day pass + monthly subscription)
- **Vercel** (hosting + serverless functions)

---

## Environment Variables

Add all of these in Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables:

| Name | Where to find it |
|------|-----------------|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` | Clerk dashboard → API Keys |
| `CLERK_SECRET_KEY` | Clerk dashboard → API Keys |
| `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY` | Stripe → Developers → API Keys |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` | Stripe → Developers → API Keys |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_URL` | Set to: `https://pacemap.co.uk` |

---

